---
import { CldImage } from 'astro-cloudinary';
---

<!-- NEW SECTION 1: THE SECRET (Krashen) - "Declassified File" Aesthetic -->
<section class='py-24 relative' id='krashen-secret'>
  <div class='max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8'>
    <!-- Section Header "Top Secret" -->
    <div class='mb-16 text-center'>
      <div
        class='inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 text-red-500 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 animate-pulse'
      >
        ⚠ Top Secret // Declassified
      </div>
      <h2
        class='text-3xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white tracking-tighter mb-4 wrap-break-word'
      >
        Rahasia yang Ingin <br />
        <span class='relative inline-block'>
          <span
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-white transform -skew-x-12 translate-y-2 opacity-10'
          ></span>
          <span
            class='relative text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-br from-white to-gray-500'
            >Dikubur Industri.</span
          >
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-20 items-start'>
      <!-- Left: The Visual Evidence -->
      <div class='relative group perspective-1000'>
        <!-- Polariod/File styling -->
        <div
          class='relative bg-white/5 border border-white/10 p-3 rounded-xl md:backdrop-blur-md transform transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:rotate-1 shadow-2xl'
        >
          <div
            class='relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden md:aspect-3/4 lg:aspect-9/16'
          >
            <CldImage
              src='Krashen_Ukio_Image_1u58f51u58f51u58_fyyfpe'
              alt='Prof. Stephen Krashen'
              width={1200}
              height={2148}
              crop='scale'
              quality='auto'
              format='auto'
              loading='eager'
              sizes='(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 50vw'
              class='w-full h-auto max-w-full! md:h-full md:object-cover filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700'
            />
            <!-- Overlay Text -->
            <div
              class='absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-6 bg-linear-to-t from-black/90 to-transparent'
            >
              <h3 class='text-white font-bold text-xl'>
                Prof. Stephen Krashen
              </h3>
              <p class='text-white/60 font-mono text-xs mt-1'>
                THE ORIGINATOR // LINGUIST // THREAT TO STATUS QUO
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Paperclip decoration -->
          <div
            class='absolute -top-4 right-10 w-4 h-12 border-2 border-gray-400 rounded-full z-20 bg-gray-800/50'
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: The Briefing -->
      <div class='space-y-8 relative'>
        <!-- Decorative line -->
        <div
          class='absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-linear-to-b from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent -ml-6 hidden lg:block'
        >
        </div>

        <div
          class='prose-lg prose-invert text-(--token-text-secondary) font-light leading-relaxed'
        >
          <p>
            sementara Meidinger dan Plötz lagi sibuk bikin "pabrik hafalan"
            penuh tabel bunpou yang bikin pusing, ada satu orang yang nemuin <strong
              class='text-white! font-bold'>kebenaran biologis sejati</strong
            > tentang cara otak manusia belajar bahasa.
          </p>
          <p>
            Dia bukan ahli bahasa biasa. Dia orang yang bikin industri buku
            pelajaran dan LPK ketar-ketir. Dalam wawancara, dia pernah bilang
            terus terang: kalau metode alami ini diterima semua orang, bakal
            jadi <span
              class='bg-red-500/20 text-red-300 px-1 py-0.5 rounded font-mono text-sm'
              >"kiamat finansial"</span
            > buat bisnis pendidikan global yang nilainya triliunan rupiah.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- EVIDENCE CARD: Twitter Embed -->
        <div
          class='skeuo-card relative overflow-hidden bg-[oklch(0.12_0.01_325)]!'
        >
          <!-- Background Spotlight (Self-Illumination) -->
          <div
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,oklch(0.586_0.246_293/0.15)_0%,transparent_70%)] pointer-events-none'
          >
          </div>
          <!-- Scanline effect -->
          <div
            class='absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(oklch(0.133_0.003_17/0)_50%,oklch(0_0_0/0.25)_50%),linear-gradient(90deg,oklch(0.628_0.258_29/0.06),oklch(0.866_0.295_142/0.02),oklch(0.452_0.313_264/0.06))] z-10 pointer-events-none bg-size-[100%_2px,3px_100%]'
          >
          </div>

          <div class='p-4 relative z-20'>
            <div
              class='flex items-center justify-between mb-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-2'
            >
              <span
                class='text-[10px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-widest'
                >EVIDENCE #2026-X</span
              >
              <span class='flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-red-500 animate-pulse'
              ></span>
            </div>

            <div
              id='twitter-embed-section'
              class='twitter-embed-container w-full max-w-full overflow-hidden'
            >
              <blockquote
                class='twitter-tweet'
                data-media-max-width='560'
                data-theme='dark'
              >
                <p lang='in' dir='ltr'>
                  Ini Kata Prof. Krashen:<br />Sebenarnya kalian kalau benar²
                  suka, dan menikmati media Jepang bisa Otodidak IMMERSE. Tanpa
                  Minna no Ningo &amp; buku Bunpou Bull5h!t<br /><br />KAREN
                  KALIAN SEMUA MALAS &amp; Tidak mau SpendTime dlm Bahasa
                  Jepang, jadi beli buku ikut LPK / Kursus / Kelas Online yg
                  S3S4D! <a href='https://t.co/rVGCLM9xvE'
                    >pic.twitter.com/rVGCLM9xvE</a
                  >
                </p>&mdash; Yoshia Kefasu (@YKefasu) <a
                  href='https://twitter.com/YKefasu/status/2015852855257915520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw'
                  >January 26, 2026</a
                >
              </blockquote>
              <style>
                /* stylelint-disable declaration-no-important */

                /* Force Twitter Embed to be responsive */
                html body .twitter-tweet,
                html body .twitter-tweet-rendered {
                  width: 100% !important;
                  min-width: 0 !important;
                  max-width: 100% !important;
                }

                /* Ensure iframe specifically scales down */
                html body iframe[id^='twitter-widget-'] {
                  width: 100% !important;
                  min-width: 0 !important;
                  max-width: 100% !important;
                }
                /* stylelint-enable declaration-no-important */
              </style>
              <!-- Load Twitter widgets.js after the entire page has loaded (waterfall complete) -->
              <script is:inline>
                (function () {
                  var target = document.getElementById('twitter-embed-section');
                  if (!target) return;

                  function loadTwitterWidget() {
                    // If widgets.js already loaded (e.g. back-forward cache), just re-render
                    if (window.twttr && window.twttr.widgets) {
                      window.twttr.widgets.load(target);
                      return;
                    }

                    var s = document.createElement('script');
                    s.src = 'https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js';
                    s.charset = 'utf-8';
                    s.async = true;
                    s.onload = function () {
                      // Explicitly render widgets after script loads
                      if (window.twttr && window.twttr.widgets) {
                        window.twttr.widgets.load(target);
                      }
                    };
                    document.head.appendChild(s);
                  }

                  // If document is already fully loaded, execute immediately
                  if (document.readyState === 'complete') {
                    setTimeout(loadTwitterWidget, 50);
                  } else {
                    // Wait for the complete waterfall (including images/resources) to finish loading
                    window.addEventListener('load', function () {
                      setTimeout(loadTwitterWidget, 50);
                    });
                  }
                })();
              </script>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='prose-lg prose-invert text-(--token-text-secondary)'>
          <h3 class='font-bold text-white! text-xl skeuo-text-emboss'>
            Kenapa?
          </h3>
          <p>
            Karena kalau semua orang tahu rahasia ini, mereka nggak perlu lagi
            beli buku tebal mahal, ikut kursus berbayar, atau hafal ribuan
            rumus—mereka bisa fasih gratis, cuma dengan cara yang otaknya memang
            dirancang.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
